## 0. App-wide implementation (tokens + layout)

- **Colours in UI:** `src/styles/globals.css` CSS variables ŌĆö avoid ad hoc `#RRGGBB` in feature code (exceptions: documented brand SVG / carrier swatch data only).
- **Routed pages:** `PageShell` (`p-6 space-y-6` default) + `PageHeader` ŌĆö override `className` for full-bleed (e.g. kanban `p-0`).
- **Tables:** `MwDataTable` / `FinancialTable` for data grids in new work.
- **Charts:** `getChartScaleColour`, `MW_CHART_COLOURS`, `MW_RECHARTS_ANIMATION`, `MW_RECHARTS_ANIMATION_BAR`, `MW_BAR_TOOLTIP_CURSOR`, `chart-theme.ts` ŌĆö see ┬¦8.5 below and `src/guidelines/DesignSystem.md` ┬¦9. Run `npm run audit:charts` before merge on chart-heavy PRs.
- **`src/lib/design-system.ts`:** `colors` is legacy; prefer CSS vars in `.tsx`.

## 1. Colours

**Crextio-aligned visual weight (~60 / ~30 / ~10):** ~60% base (canvas, white cards, neutral-50ŌĆō100), ~30% content/chrome (neutral text, Mirage headlines, default icon wells on light), ~10% **yellow thread** (primary CTA, active nav, key KPI accent, chart 67ŌĆō100% band, Ōēż1ŌĆō2 yellow `IconWell`s per viewport). Mirage carries contrast; yellow is continuity, not fill-everywhere.

**MW Yellow thread:** use sparingly for wayfinding and one primary action per section ŌĆö not yellow body text or rainbow KPIs.

**Icon wells (Lucide `strokeWidth={1.5}`):** on light ŌåÆ Mirage well + white icon; on dark ŌåÆ light grey well + Mirage icon; **key** ŌåÆ yellow well + Mirage icon (rare). Prefer `IconWell` / `KpiStatCard` `iconSurface`.

**Chart scale 0ŌĆō100:** `getChartScaleColour` ŌĆö 0ŌĆō33% low grey, 34ŌĆō66% Mirage, 67ŌĆō100% mw-yellow (`chart-scale-*` tokens).

MW Yellow (brand accent ŌĆö 10% of UI):
- `mw-yellow-50`: #FFFBF0 ŌĆö selected row bg, subtle highlight
- `mw-yellow-100`: #FFF3D6 ŌĆö text selection highlight
- `mw-yellow-200`: #FFE8AD ŌĆö warning alert border
- `mw-yellow-300`: #FFDB7A
- `mw-yellow-400`: #FFCF4B ŌĆö **primary CTA**, active states, checked controls
- `mw-yellow-500`: #F2BF30 ŌĆö hover on primary
- `mw-yellow-600`: #E6A600 ŌĆö active/pressed on primary
- `mw-yellow-700`: #CC8E00
- `mw-yellow-800`: #A67300
- `mw-yellow-900`: #805900

Grey scale (30% structure):
- Near Black `#0A0A0A` ŌĆö headlines, primary text, active icons
- Dark `#2C2C2C` ŌĆö body text, text on yellow buttons
- Mid `#525252` ŌĆö table body, descriptions
- Medium `#737373` ŌĆö labels, captions, inactive icons (minimum text colour)
- Border `#E5E5E5` ŌĆö card borders, dividers
- Subtle `#F5F5F5` ŌĆö page background, input bg
- Warm `#F8F7F4` ŌĆö grouped card bg inside sheets
- White `#FFFFFF` ŌĆö card backgrounds (60%)

Neutral scale aliases: `neutral-50` (#FAFAFA) through `neutral-900` (#0A0A0A).

Dark accent: `mw-mirage` #1A2732 ŌĆö dark variant buttons, dark badges, sidebar bg.
Off-white: `mw-off-white` #F8F7F4.

Status (dots/badges only, never card backgrounds):
- Success: #36B37E
- Info: #0052CC
- Warning: #FACC15
