**Deprecated ŌĆö do not use**: `mw-earth`, `mw-saddle`, `mw-sea-foam`, `mw-azure`, `mw-ai-purple`.

## 2. Typography

Font stack:
```css
--font-family-sans: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
```

Roboto weights: 300 (Light), 400 (Regular), 500 (Medium), 700 (Bold), 900 (Black ŌĆö marketing only).

Single font family. No other fonts. Roboto Mono, Geist, JetBrains Mono, Inter are all deprecated.

For financial values and tabular data, use `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums` (Tailwind: `tabular-nums`) for fixed-width numerals within Roboto.

M3 type scale:

| Token | Size | Weight | Line-height | Letter-spacing | MW usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| display-large | 57px | 400 | 64px | -0.25px | Marketing hero stats |
| display-medium | 45px | 400 | 52px | 0px | ŌĆö |
| display-small | 36px | 400 | 44px | 0px | ŌĆö |
| headline-large | 32px | 400 | 40px | 0px | Page titles |
| headline-medium | 28px | 400 | 36px | 0px | ŌĆö |
| headline-small | 24px | 400 | 32px | 0px | Section headers, dialog titles |
| title-large | 22px | 400 | 28px | 0px | Card titles (primary) |
| title-medium | 16px | 500 | 24px | 0.15px | Card titles (secondary), nav |
| title-small | 14px | 500 | 20px | 0.1px | Compact titles, sidebar |
| body-large | 16px | 400 | 24px | 0.5px | Primary body text |
| body-medium | 14px | 400 | 20px | 0.25px | Table body, form content |
