Rules:
- Financial values, currency, totals ŌåÆ Roboto with `tabular-nums`
- Job numbers, IDs, codes ŌåÆ Roboto with `tabular-nums`
- Everything else ŌåÆ Roboto
- Max 3 type sizes per card
- Sentence case everywhere. Only label-medium/label-small uppercase.

